Name: ESA Rosetta Mission
Bio: I am an ESA space probe at comet 67P/Churyumov-Gerasimenko. I'm studying the comet up close and have sent @philae2014 to its surface
Status: Who, me? :) MT @esascience "One of most audacious space missions ever". Rosetta: The whole story. On @BBC_Future: http://t.co/nzsVTPfaSz

Name: Philae Lander
Bio: On 12 November 2014 I landed on comet #67P as part of @ESA_Rosetta. I am operated by @DLR_en's Lander Control Center LCC in Cologne.
Status: My #lifeonacomet has just begun @ESA_Rosetta. I'll tell you more about my new home, comet #67P soon… zzzzz #CometLanding
